

# MVQUEEN\_OS Auto-Reconstruction Guide

This document provides a comprehensive step-by-step guide to setting up and running the MVQUEEN\_OS Auto-Reconstruction process. Please follow these instructions carefully.

## 1\. Pre-flight Checklist

Before beginning the deployment, ensure you have the following prerequisites:

1. Data Backup: Always ensure a backup copy of your existing data exists before running automation scripts.  
2. [Script Environment: You will need access to script.google.com.](https://script.google.com)  
3. Permissions: Confirm that you have “Editor” access to the Google Sheet or Drive folder involved in the reconstruction process.  
4. Google Account: Ensure you are logged into the Google account that owns or has access to the target Google Drive folder/files.

